{% extends "base.njk" %}
{% block content %}
    <div class="container mx-auto px-9 max-w-screen-xl mb-5 mb-5">
        <h1 class="my-20 text-3xl font-extrabold leading-none tracking-tight text-gray-900 md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl dark:text-white">
            Accessing support</h1>
        <p class="mt-3">
            This page summarises how a Sport Wales project concept can reach the Digital & Service Design (D&SD) Team and from
            there, how the team’s support and skills can be accessed to develop a solution to a problem which the project is planned
            to solve.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold my-4">The process</h2>
        <p>
            If you have a project which you feel would resolve a
            <a href="https://www.nngroup.com/articles/problem-statements/" target="blank" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">‘problem’</a>
            or improve a service, then it will be worth exploring this with the D&SD team.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
            Please fill the ‘Project Request Form’ (PRF),
            <a href="project-request-form.html" target="blank" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">available here</a>, with as much information as you can, to tell us
                about what you have in mind! This will enable a good starting point for a conversation. From there we can use the
                following steps to determine how the team could help with delivering the project.
        </p>
        {% include 'includes/process-cards.njk' %}
    </div>
{% endblock %}